ehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果打飛機有得傾，其他戒有冇得傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打飛機又冇害人，點解算係罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聖經係咪無誤與絕對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基督教究竟合唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會神根本唔係聖經所講咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a77e0476e61ec938992e1ad89cbfd5b9c3a5886","tid":787664,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"打飛機算唔算性行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2202d98efd79b06c8c45922bfa2a1bba1218e063","tid":787664,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"耶穌話凡向婦女動淫念，咁已經犯姦淫<br />\n所以正常嚟講，基督徒弟兄唔可以打飛機"},{"pid":"db3d6d0a914d2e5ede3252732b1f15497489c442","tid":787664,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2202d98efd79b06c8c45922bfa2a1bba1218e063","tid":787664,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"耶穌話凡向婦女動淫念，咁已經犯姦淫<br />\n所以正常嚟講，基督徒弟兄唔可以打飛機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"咁如果我打飛機個陣冇向婦女動淫念 又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7af59941e53ba8cdf0646b3506f72dfdd0e93b","tid":787664,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db3d6d0a914d2e5ede3252732b1f15497489c442","tid":787664,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2202d98efd79b06c8c45922bfa2a1bba1218e063","tid":787664,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"耶穌話凡向婦女動淫念